Tech Stack – Web Application
🖥️ Frontend
React.js – Component-based web UI framework

Tailwind CSS – Utility-first CSS for responsive, clean design

Framer Motion – For smooth animations and transitions

Recharts – For visualizing mood trends and emotional data

Lottie + Heroicons – Animated UI elements for user engagement

🌐 Backend
Node.js + Express.js – RESTful API server

MongoDB Atlas – Cloud NoSQL database for mood logs and metadata

Mongoose – ODM for schema design and queries

Cloudinary / Firebase Storage – For storing user-uploaded voice/video securely

🧠 AI/ML Services
Python (FastAPI) – Serving AI models via API

Facial Emotion Detection – OpenCV + TensorFlow

Voice Emotion Analysis – PyTorch + DeepSpeech

Text Sentiment Analysis – Transformers (BERT / RoBERTa via HuggingFace)

Model Orchestration – Dockerized services for modular deployment

🔐 Security
JWT Authentication – Secure user login/session control

AES Encryption – End-to-end encryption of mood logs

Helmet.js + Rate Limiting – Backend protection from attacks

🚀 Deployment
Vercel / Netlify – Frontend hosting

Render / Railway / Heroku – For backend + model APIs

Docker + GitHub Actions – For CI/CD and scalable container-based deployment
